OL,3,CRoad safety campaigner dresses up as
OL,4,Ctraffic cone in speeding vigil
OL,6,FA road safety campaigner has dressed
OL,7,Fup as a traffic cone to keep her
OL,8,Fcommunity safe.
OL,10,FFaye Davies from Seaside in Llanelli
OL,11,Fhas dressed in this bright outfit to
OL,12,Fencourage drivers passing through her
OL,13,Fresidential street to slow down and
OL,14,Ffollow the speed limit.
OL,16,FThis week she has given up 24 hours of
OL,17,Fher time to complete a road safety
OL,18,Fvigil to raise awareness.
