OL,3,CRoad safety campaigner dresses up as
OL,4,Ctraffic cone in speeding vigil
OL,6,FFaye Davies who is campaigning for
OL,7,FRoad Safety said: "If you stood here
OL,8,Ffor half an hour, it's absolutely
OL,9,Fshocking. That's why I've taken
OL,10,Faction. The countless times I've seen
OL,11,Fa child almost being knocked over and
OL,12,FI work full time but I've still seen
OL,13,Fso many near misses because it's not
OL,14,Fjust a normal street, it's one of the
OL,15,Fmain roads down to Llanelli beach."
OL,17,FFaye says the support she's received
OL,18,Ffrom locals has been very positive.
