OL,3,CRoad safety campaigner dresses up as
OL,4,Ctraffic cone in speeding vigil
OL,6,FMany residents here say drivers
OL,7,Fspeeding along this road has been an
OL,8,Fongoing issue for a number of years.
OL,10,FChris Rees-Andrews, a Local Pub
OL,11,FLandlord said: "We hear cars all hours
OL,12,Fof the day and night. The speed at
OL,13,Fwhich some of them travel is more than
OL,14,F60-70mph on ocassion. It is
OL,15,Fhorrendous. Only this morning, I could
OL,16,Fhear a car screeching on the
OL,17,Froundabout."
