OL,6,FFaye has been in touch with local
OL,7,Fcouncillors and road safety charities
OL,8,Fto review the situation on Marine
OL,9,FStreet.
OL,11,FMeanwhile, she will carry on
OL,12,Fcampaigning in her traffic cone outfit
OL,13,Fand encourage drivers to watch their
OL,14,Fspeed in residential areas like this.
OL,16,FITV Wales has approached Dyfed Powys
OL,17,FPolice for a statement.
